{"tid":2128703,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳智思稱沒有聽聞政府討論押後選舉　未知政府如何處理","createTime":"2020-07-28T06:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T07:26:06.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"cebbb76d77615389e5c1755172cece3c3840862b","tid":2128703,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:31:06.000Z","msg":"行政會議召集人陳智思接受本台訪問，被問到政府有否討論延遲選舉，他表示沒有，亦沒有聽聞有關的討論。<br />\n<br />\n被問到政府是否有意延遲9月的立法會選舉，陳智思表示，未知政府會如何處理選舉的安排，現時處理疫情問題更為重要。他又說，疫情無法控制，選舉亦無法拉票，會影響整個選舉效果，相信政府要作考慮，但認為延遲選舉的事，言之尚早。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540324-20200728.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540324-20200728.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBgogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=273659de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540324-20200728.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=77690193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540324-20200728.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"7440e06871b6b717f322e5b8ffde1d065511e75e","tid":2128703,"uid":37487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:31:31.000Z","msg":"唔做正契弟"},{"pid":"2c1831da5d32ea3c6d4fc7adbe54b608f4576377","tid":2128703,"uid":91317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:32:19.000Z","msg":"即係又放風, 搵次決斷D得唔得"},{"pid":"e5cc4554375f23f63de1408574c3162524a20b5e","tid":2128703,"uid":4285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:33:23.000Z","msg":"傾嗰時無你份喳？"},{"pid":"c7b191f945c86665201cce234bcd61c94470938c","tid":2128703,"uid":57674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:34:06.000Z","msg":"又放風試水溫啊? 屌你老母縮撚到咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f78f4b90d7f7b729e73c5fce670d45f4d41361","tid":2128703,"uid":88133,"like":2